<p><strong>The volume of a cylinder is a quantity present in many applicati=
ons</strong>. For example, in a vehicle, the <strong><span>engine displacem=
ent</span></strong> term refers to the volume swept by the piston in the en=
gine cylinders, multiplied by the number of cylinders.</p>
<p>This tool calculates the cylinder volume in a matter of seconds. Still, =
<strong>in the following sections, we present the cylinder volume formula</=
strong> to do it manually, including the equation to calculate the volume o=
f a hollow cylinder.</p>
<p>To know more about the different volume units, you can look at our <a hr=
ef=3D"https://www.calctool.org/conversion/volume-conversion" class=3D"js-li=
nk">volume converter</a>.</p>
</div></div><div class=3D"jsx-1030690091 contentPartPromo"><div><div id=3D"=
