<li>The cylinder volume should be <strong>1570.8 cm<sup>3</sup></strong>. T=
hat's how you find the volume of a cylinder with this calculator.</li>
</ol>
<p>How to calculate the volume of a <strong>hollow cylinder</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Input the height</strong> of the cylinder in the "Height" box. =
